.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-ALIAS-SET" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-alias-set \- update the node's gossip alias at runtime
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-alias-set
.I alias
.SH DESCRIPTION
Calls
.B lightning-cli setconfig alias
to update the announced alias without restarting the daemon.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable or the command is unsupported.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-alias (1),
.BR lightning-node-config (1)
